headline: Major airline stocks getting lift from renewed travel demand
summary: Major airline stocks — like United Airlines (UAL) and Delta Air Lines (DAL) — have experienced some serious gains in 2024 as demand returns to the travel industry and operators. Yahoo Finance senior business reporter Ines Ferré highlights several drivers behind growing travel demand and international bookings. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here. This post was written by Luke Carberry Mogan.
